  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div xml:id="KT185-kilavi">
          <p type="edition">talaimakaṉ irā vantoḻukāniṉṟa kālattu vēṟupaṭṭa talaimakaḷai “vēṟupaṭṭāyāl” eṉṟāṭkuk kiḻatti uraittatu.</p>
          <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Told by HER to the one who said “you have changed indeed” to HER, who had changed in a time when HE kept coming to night trysts.</p>
          </div>
          

        <div xml:id="KT185">
            <lg type="edition">
<l>                nutalpacap pivarntu titalai vāṭi</l>
<l>                neṭumeṉ paṇaitōḷ cāayt toṭinekiḻn</l>
<l>                tiṉṉa ḷākuta ṉummiṟ ṟākumeṉac</l>
<l>                colli ṉevaṉān tōḻi palvarip</l>
<l>                pāmpupai yavintatu pōlak kūmpik</l>
<l>                koṇṭaliṟ ṟolainta voṇceṅ kāntaḷ</l>
<l>                kaṉmicaik kaviyu nāṭaṟke</l>
<l>                ṉaṉmā mēṉi yaḻipaṭar nilaiyē.</l>
             </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
           <l rend="indent">“Pallor spread on the forehead, beauty spots faded,</l>
           <l rend="indent">long soft bamboo shoulders emaciated, bracelets become loose</l>
           <l rend="indent">– that she is like this is your doing!”,</l>
           <l>if someone speaks [like this]</l>
           <l rend="indent">about the state of destructive affliction in my good dark body</l>
           <l rend="indent">to the man from a land, where the stony height</l>
           <l rend="indent">is covered by bright red Malabar lilies, lost in the east wind</l>
           <l rend="indent">[and] closing, shrunk like the hood of the many-striped snake</l>
           <l rend="indent3">what [might] happen, friend?</l>
           </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
